\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
No.. Because - let me put it this way, that - when my mother was alive - my sister was only a baby like as it were you see and - very, very - at Kindergarten you see and when me mother - when - w
hen my mother died she - she went to stay with an aunt of mine, this - this aunt in Aigburth until such time as we got a house - just adjacent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
