\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What time would that have been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well it differed I suppose as we got older I - in the - in the every early days of course you didn't go out after tea. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3298693\charrsid11093751 And - later it became seven, eight, and then I should started to go to the gymnasium and - I was 
