\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well - I had me breakfast about half past eight before I went to school.
