ng we'd have that but it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3298693\charrsid11093751 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Yorkshire}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 {\*\xmlclose}
 pud. And that was put onto your plate with the - with the warm gravy on and you had that prior to your - potato - meat and potatoes and that, yes.
