\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You hadn't any time for games. It was mission hall of a morning. Sunday school of an afternoon and mission hal
l at night. There was no time left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What was there feeling though if you wanted to go out for a little while and play in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh well I used to be dressed up - when I got a bit older like in my - in my - you know, eleven, twelve so on - I
 - you had to have your best suit on and - the bane of my life was I had to wear cuffs - celluloid cuffs. And as soon as we got outside I always managed to find some paper from somewhere and I used to - carefully wrap these cuffs and stick 'em up a spout 
- outside the house at the end of the street - up a spout. But once or twice I was caught out when it rained.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Your parents attended a place of worship too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 I went - I - they went as a rule on a Sunday night. Sunday evening. They went on a Sunday 
night more than a - a family - family gathering you see, they would come over and take the dear old lady.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 The granny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes. For the granny. A couple of her sisters, mother and dad would go there. And as a special treat, if there was something spe
cial on I was allowed to accompany them. The object of going to the mission hall and the - this kind of thing - also the Band of Hope on a Friday night - was to get a stamp on your card and you could go to the Sunday school treat or mission hall treat. Th
is is a very similar thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What sort of things did you do for the Sunday school treats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Barnstone Dale and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  Barnstone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Dale was the - the great place. Otherwise some - we used to go over to - perhaps over to Eastham Woods, there was a great plac
e there we used to - we used to assemble - march down to the Dingle car sheds where several tramcars would be put at our disposal and the kids'd be on top and - and inside like, waving and all this kind of thing, down to the Pierhead. We'd be }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 marshalled}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  onto a boat and then - that was to Secombe. Get up from Secombe to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6630985\charrsid11093751 R}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
ailway Station at Secombe I think it's closed now, I don't know, and then we'd go on to Barnstone Dale and various places - quite local and - there'd be - tables and - trestles and forms set out in big marquees, they specialized in this kind of thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What other social activities organized by the mission hall - what was the proper tile of the church you went to - was it a Baptist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh no, well - it was - I don't know what the - Admiral Street Mission Hall of a morning. St Silas or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place
}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}St John's{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} Sunday school of the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What denomination would St Silas be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 St Silas was church of England. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What about the evening one - that would be the mission again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 That - well, this was another mission - St Silas Mission Hall of an evening.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What social activities organized by these various paces did you take part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes, Band of Hope on a Friday night. Oh well I used to - as I got a bit older I say - I cou
ldn't join under twelve but as soon as I was twelve I joined the Florence Institute and they used to use the - the gymnasium. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did you belong to the choir at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Personally - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did the St Silas Church of England or St Silas Mission a hall or the other Mission Hall run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, not at the time. Price}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6630985\charrsid11093751 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 s Gate Baptist church ran the - ran the Band of Hope on the Friday evening. It's now a Norwegian church by the way. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church or the mission?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 In - well - for a main meal say Saturday - Sunday - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Who would say it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Father. Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did you ever have family prayers together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
No. No, you said your own prayers you see, you were taught your own prayers by - by your mother and then you got on with it. 'Cos I know my sister could never say she used to like a very simple praye
r the first one, Gentle Jesus, meek and milk, look upon a little child. Pity my simplicity, suffer me to come to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6630985\charrsid11093751  thee.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
 But - she could never say simplicity - she always said pretty cissie. Well and all she got was pity my pretty cissie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did your father take an interest in politics and do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well I know what his views were, yes, he was a Conservative. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Why do you think he held that view?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well because the main Conservatives in the town were the main people in the Dock Board.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And this influenced him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 An - oh well that - like that was his work and if he was ever found out I suppose that he was - he was attached to some other - party -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Would this have affected his employment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well that was
 what he thought - that was his idea. Whether it did or not in those days - I just wouldn't say, but he thought it would. Or he thought it might.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 This was bringing pressure on himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes. Yes, he said, one of my father's big troubles was, w
hen the Conservatives were in power there was always plenty of work. And he wasn't only speaking for himself - like for other people that he knew. When they were in power - when the people in - in power were Conservatives they were the money people and th
ey - they called the tune and if you're going to disrupt them well - you - you're just going to make - make a whip for your own back.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What about your mother - did she take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What do you think her views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
She never expressed any. And - I think if she was entitled to vote she'd have - just followed the old - whatever the old man said. Yes, I think a woman was very much - I don't think she was permitted to think for herself. I', not saying that a man - he - 
you know - yes, I think they would take his word for it. That he'd say - that's the way my bread's buttered, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did your parents talk about any issues or if they had any views who should govern the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 country}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  and if they felt the working man had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 raw}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  deal - can you remember them talking about things like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
I know he used - he had - there was some - he knew a lot of - he knew a lot of poverty, he didn't suffer it himself but he - his eldest brother, who was a bit of a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 harum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  scarum bloke, he had been all his life, he was only a dock labourer. And he was lucky if he got above two days work a week kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And did your father feel strongly about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Do you remember your parents voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes. Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And your mother would have voted too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh she would have voted ex - exactly the same as my dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And she would have voted Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You mentioned that your father felt he would be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 safer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  voting Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Would you say your father felt himself under any pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 That's what I say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You really feel that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 As - you see, he'd been made a foreman }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 shipwright}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 Dock Board}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
 and he thought if he incurred their displeasure by - even - you know, giving - any other than a Conservative opinion on a thing it might have clapped on him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Was your father a member of the political party - do you remember him working for any of the parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Or your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did they take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well as I say -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 I know your father had a hard day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1182239\charrsid11093751 Yes, and he used to - have a doze for say an hour after dinner, he might on the sofa like ways and as he 
