\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How many times a week would he go out do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh, just a couple of nights. Especially on a Saturday night, he always spent a Saturday night from about {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 8}}}eight o'clock{\*\xmlclose}
 with a brother-in-law of his that was - a master baker because he was free that night you see. That - yes, but otherwise this chap'd
 be at work every other night you see. That's right. So Saturday night they - they had a rendezvous and they used to meet up with - they used to pick up Jim about {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}
{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 8}}}eight o'clock{\*\xmlclose} and they used to go to a local.
