\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No. I - I've never come across that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You went straight to school - you weren't taught at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No. Five years of age I went to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 When you first started what time of the morning did you go and when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 51}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}
{\xmlattrvalue 11}}}Nine 'til twelve{\*\xmlclose}. And then - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 30}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 13}}}one thirty to four{\*\xmlclose}
. And that - that's carried on right through school, yes. The same age for - the same times for infants and as for the other classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You didn't start just in the mornings and then graduate to all day school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 A Church of England school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How did you get to school and how long did it take you?
