\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How was that - you'd changed schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, I'd just moved from Trebord Street to R}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6975372\charrsid11093751 hiwlas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  Street, just further down the - South Street, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Who went with you when you first started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 I couldn't tell you that. Probably my - well - I suppose my mother went an
d - fixed up everything so I was in school for the first day and I certainly knew - knew my way home. I only had to come out of the side gate from school, walk fifty yards and through a passage and into the house.
