\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
