\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Can you tell me anything about that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Well certain amounts of gang - gang warfare from different parts. Yes. They would say - refer to us as the - the South Street gang as against - the High Park Street or North Hill or Admiral Street gang - like - you had to affiliate to eith
er one or other - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes, some - I could point out one chap that I see as a regular thing. A bit of a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 pansy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  like - we looked upon him as and - yet he's been quite a successful chap. He's 
now - seventy-one - years of age - seventy-one going on - seventy-two and he still hasn't - hasn't retired. He's retired from full time work but he's still quite an important person in the - Stock and Share market. That's why people - that go to him for a
dvice and - he still - apart from working he still kind of - sells advice kind of thing, or gives advice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And he was a bit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 pansy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  like was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes, very pansified kind of boy you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Would this be the kind of boy mainly who would be left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Well he was - you know - well you know what I mean by a - a - a pansy boy. Actually I think - he should have been a girl if you follow what I mean - possibly he was an only child, I just wouldn't know but I imagine so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You didn't go on to another school afterwards did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, no. No, no. Not even night school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How old were you when you left school - you said fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Well I - yes. I left - like a week before I was fourteen. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
No, I wanted to work. Yes. I - I couldn't go any - any higher in school, I'd - I'd spent over - I'd spent eighteen months in the top class and I couldn't go any - any higher so there was nothing else they could be taught to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 So there was no purpose in staying on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No. And I didn't wish }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6975372\charrsid11093751 to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  enter for - for scholarships - to the colleges or any of those, I wasn't interested in that, I wanted to - have a commercial career. As I - I - I was keen on 
going into shipping, may father said well I could go into shipping but he really wanted me to enter for the Civil Service. And my object was to get into shipping - into shipping and go away as a pur - like finish up as a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 purser}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 , that was my - object.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You didn't attend any part time education after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No. None whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh from attending school - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You feel it set you in good stead?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Yes. Can I give you one very good example. We never had - hours of - of homework and that business. Before we left at say ten minutes to four before the general assembly at school there was always a general 
assembly at five to four you see. Just sang - the day thou gave us Lord is ended, and then you dismissed but they'd pull the screens back. Some cases there were only curtains to pull back but there was a main screen that divided the hall. One teacher woul
d play the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 piano}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
 and then the whole school would join in this - sing the hymn. Right. Now - but - say five minutes prior to - prior to general assembly the teacher wrote ten words on the blackboard - and every boy copied them into a homework book and your j
ob then was to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 syllabif}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6975372\charrsid11093751 y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
 these words as would pronounce them or spell them as the case - and then you would put the meaning of those words and say from the age of - say the last five years when you'd done ten words a night. One's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 vocabulary}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  became twice as extensive at least as the ordinary person in the street.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Was this a particular thing that this one teacher did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh well it was first established by the head - Edmund Burke - he afterwards }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 left}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  and went to take over a new Morrison school that was built then. He was an M.A. Oxford and all this kind of thing, he was one of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 Esparantoists}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
, he was - the - they'd just started this, Esperanto cult and - he was one of the leadings lights on it. He also wrote - composed several songs. That kind of thing. Oh yes, he was a very bright - chap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 That was an excellent }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 idea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Well I think so. Period of say five years. Say forty weeks for five - and you done ten a night and - in - ordinary committee kind of thing. Now we had a chairman that insisted that it was his }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 prerogative}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  to do this, that, oh well, that is my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 prerogative}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  and you take him aside and say, Bill, you're making a fool }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 of}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
 yourself - it's prerogative. No it's not. Pound on it any time you like. And that's the kind of thing tha
t you get. I made a suggestion, he said, oh I'm a bit sceptical about that. Well then you take him aside after, say, Bill, why do you make such a bloody idiot of yourself. Why? You mean sceptical. No, sceptical.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Whilst you were at school did you have a part time job or any means or earning a little extra money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Yes. I used to take out milk from seven to eight of a morning and - a couple of the deliveries at the school. 'Course you - you took out milk then in a big can, and by the way, milk was a penny }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12391602\charrsid11093751 farthing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  a pint - tuppence ha'penny a quart, they used to shout in the street. But I worked for a firm in High Park Street, J }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9337984 &}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  K Foster, I had about - eight people to serve of a morning and you had your big can and a couple of small cans round and y
ou just dug in and got - a pint or two pints, knocked at the door and poured it into their jug and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How did you get that job - through your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh no. Just talk amongst the lads. Somebody - somebody giving it up or leaving school and going to work full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And you worked an hour in the morning and an hour in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 No, half an hour in the evening. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And an hour in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes. For which I got one shilling per week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did this include Saturdays and Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
Oh - now let - oh yes, for Saturdays and Sundays just the same. And I don't think we went out on a Sunday afternoon - I don't think - Sat - Saturday and Sunday afternoons, I don't think so, I think they had to take whatever they wanted for the
 day. Yes. Because I - I know I used to draw the - the church organ as well. I got a bob a week for blowing the church organ - I used to blow that. You had to work the bellows in those days and - and when he got on the - on the basso profundo I might - us
e
d to have to - fairly go. You see, he went up a scale which showed you the amount of air pressure kind of thing and - when he got on this, you know - there were times when you had to go you see and he used to practice - two nights a week for an hour. Mayb
e the choir also }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3695530\charrsid11093751 was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  with him but - you were just in the - in this place. And - oh you had to keep it up - you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 AND you did this on the Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 On the Sunday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And the two days in the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And how did you get that - just the same sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
I - the same thing, just talk amongst the boys - somebody else was giving it up. I suppose he got another job or he'd got some other interest and - so you go along and see the organist, actually I went along to see the -
 the - the - the, you know, Minister. You - you'd go along and - you got a - you got a shilling a week for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 So you earned two shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Two bob a week I earned - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 If you were off on holiday would you have been paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3695530\charrsid11093751 
Oh well I would - I would have to get - when - it was quite understood that you had to find a substitute and you'd - it was the substitute that would - suit your boss or whoever it was - you had to take them along, say, this is a pal of mine, Sid J
ones, lived 120 Admiral Street and he's offered to do my job while I'm away for next week or fortnight.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 So you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3695530\charrsid11093751 wouldn't}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid864932\charrsid11093751  get paid - that person would get the money for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Gave it all. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Would she have given any back to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 A penny a week off my father, penny a week off my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 This made no difference to your pocket money whether you were earning or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 You still got this penny a week back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 And your mother would have put it into the housekeeping would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 I suppose so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How did you get on with the other people you worked with or were you working on your own on the milk round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Just entirely on -
 on my own and I went there - there in the morning and they might give me say two gallons of milk, I don't know the amounts now, give it to me in my - in my main can and you had your - and you had the other cans round you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How did your employer treat you - Mr Foster did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14963447 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8157651 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid864932\charrsid11093751 How did he treat you and how did you feel about him?
\par 
